title: Infinix Smart 5A (Quetzal Cyan, 32 GB)  (2 GB RAM)

product_specification.In The Box: Handset, Adaptor, USB Cable, TPU Case, Protective Screen Guard, Quick Start Guide, Warranty Card
product_specification.Other Display Features: 20:9 Aspect Ratio, 500 NITS Brightness, 90.5% Screen-to-body Ratio, Eye Care Mode, 1200:1 Contrast Ratio, AGC AS2 Glass Protection
product_specification.Operating Frequency: 2G GSM: B2/B3/B5/B8, 3G WCDMA: B1/B5/B8; 4G LTE: B1/B3/B5/B8/B38/B40/B41
product_specification.Primary Camera Features: 8MP Dual AI Rear Camera (f 2.0), Triple LED Flash, Picture Modes: 18 Auto Scene Detection, Custom Bokeh, AI HDR, AI 3D Beauty, Panorama, Video Features: FHD Video Recording
product_specification.Secondary Camera Features: 8MP (f 2.0) AI Front Camera with Dual LED Flash, Front Camera Modes: AI HDR, AI 3D Beauty, WideSelfie, Portrait, Auto Filters, Video Features: FHD Video Recording
product_specification.Flash: Rear -Triple LED Flash | Front - Dual LED Flash
product_specification.Sensors: Fingerprint Sensor, Ambient Light Sensor, G-Sensor, Proximity Sensor
product_specification.Other Features: Power Marathon Tech, Video Assistant, Game Zone, Social Turbo, Xhide, Theft Alert, Peek Proof, Secure Card, Kids Mode, Bike Mode, 360 Flashlight, Smart Gestures, Photo Editor, AI Gallery, Battery Saver, Face and Fingerprint Unlock, Dual VoLTE
product_specification.Audio Formats: AAC, AAC+, AAC+ Enhanced, OGG Vorbis, WAV, MP3, Midi
product_specification.Warranty Summary: 1 Year on Handset and 6 Months on Accessories

product_description.Immersive Visuals: The Infinix Smart 5A comes with an impressive 16.5 cm (6.52) HD+ screen with a Drop-notch display and a 20:9 aspect ratio. The narrow bezels mean that this smartphone has a screen to body ratio of 90.5%. Additionally, it has up to 500 nits of brightness 1200:1 contrast ratio, which helps in improving your visual experience as a whole.
product_description.Battery Backup: This smartphone is powered by a 5000 mAh battery that offers up to 19 hours of video playback, 121 hours of music playback, 33 hours of talk-time on 4G, 16 hours of web browsing, 13 hours of gaming, and 35 days of standby time. It also features Power Marathon technology that can improve the battery life by up to 25%.
product_description.Smart Unlock Features: The Infinix Smart 5A features a multifunctional fingerprint sensor for added security of this device. It also comes with a swift Face Unlock feature that takes less than a second to unlock your phone.
product_description.Dual Rear Camera: This smartphone comes with an AI-powered 8 MP dual rear camera and triple LED flash. The f 2.0 aperture of the camera and the Auto Scene detection feature help it automatically recognise up to 18 different outdoor scenarios. It can not only capture Full HD videos, but it also features Custom Bokeh, AI HDR, AI 3D Beauty, Panorama mode, and more.
product_description.8 MP Selfie Camera: The Infinix Smart 5A features an 8 MP selfie camera with dedicated dual-LED flash and an f/2.0 aperture. Additionally, it also features AI HDR, AI 3D Beauty, WideSelfie, Portrait, and Auto Filters.
product_description.Quad-core Processor: This smartphone features 2 GB of RAM, along with up to 32 GB of memory, powered by a 12 nm Helio A20 1.8 GHz Quad-core processor. The phone features a dedicated Dual 4G SIM slot and an SD card slot, giving you the option of extending the phone’s memory up to 256 GB. This smartphone supports Dual VoLTE calling, as well as VoWiFI calling.
product_description.Fashionable Design: The Infinix Smart 5A features an elegant Prism design with a beautiful flow pattern at the back. The narrow bezel design, 8.75 mm thickness, and 183 gm weight give this phone an exquisite yet fashionable look.
product_description.DTS Surround Sound: This smartphone comes with DTS-HD Surround Sound for an immersive aural experience.
product_description.Smooth UI and Operating System: This smartphone runs on XOS 7.6 operating system that is powered by Android 11 (Go Edition). It comes with loads of helpful features, such as the Video Assistant, Game Zone, Social Turbo, Xhide, Theft Alert, Peek Proof, Secure Card, Kids Mode, Bike Mode, 360 Flashlight, Smart Gestures, Eye Care, Photo Editor, AI Gallery, and more.
